messages.messageBody:
Cool, Deborah, I am jealous! We can't even do that here.

We'll probably end up standing with the masses and usually get turned away the first tries!

On Sunday our family will be helping with a Pre-Potter Party at our Science Center to get us geared up. The kids worked on robotics projects the last 3 Saturdays that have Harry Potter as a theme. My daughter and I built a robotic owl, my son built the flying car, pretty fun!!

We are counting down the days,
And of course to the Two Towers too!

Take Care,
Kelli
